===Etymology===
[[bridi]] + [[valsi]]

===[[Brivla]]===
x<sup>1</sup> '''brivla''' x<sup>2</sup> x<sup>3</sup> x<sup>4</sup>

# '''x<sup>1</sup>''' is a [[predicate]] word expressing relation '''x<sup>2</sup>''' among [[argument]]s '''x<sup>3</sup>''' in language '''x<sup>4</sup>'''

